id: pm-ibyi
title: Extract shared legacy settings test fixtures
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: jscpd found tests/unit/settings-store.spec.ts repeats large legacy settings JSON fixtures inside the same spec. Representative clone: settings-store.spec.ts:82-104 vs settings-store.spec.ts:251-273, with repeated output/search/providers/vector_store defaults plus only small workflow/item_format scenario differences. Existing pm-v798 covers production item-type normalization and pm-axd1 covers extension policy defaults, but no active item covers settings-store fixture duplication. Fix by adding a local helper such as writeLegacySettings(pmRoot, overrides) or legacySettingsFixture(overrides), so tests express only the missing/explicit fields under test."
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 3
tags[4]: code-quality,dedup,settings,tests
