updated_at: "2026-05-22T19:09:25.444Z"
author: codex-dup-audit
acceptance_criteria: settings-store specs use a shared legacy settings fixture builder with explicit per-test overrides; behavior under test remains visible for omitted workflow and item_format metadata cases; settings-store tests and pnpm build pass.
